{"tid":1190691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【禍不單行】男子西貢被青竹蛇咬腳 再遇交通意外傷上加傷","createTime":"2019-06-07T13:02:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T13:55:36.000Z","uid":54373,"like":781,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"77e3655d4a170c8cc2bcb216c76b9650ff8a5e91","tid":1190691,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T13:02:03.000Z","msg":"早上10時44分，西貢伙頭墳洲香港晨曦會戒毒所兩名男院友，在院舍內除草期間，其中姓鍾（25歲）院友被青竹蛇咬傷右腳腳指，另一院友見狀報警，約半小時後，4名男院友（年齡27至50歲）用三輪車載送鍾往伙頭墳洲碼頭等候救援期間，三輪車突失控撞向一草叢，5人全部受傷，被蛇咬傷腳的鍾傷上加傷，可謂禍不單行，而姓吳（49歲）院友更被蜜蜂刺傷。鍾與另一名院友先行由政府飛行服務隊吊送往東區醫院救治，其餘3名車禍中傷者，送到水警東基地，再由救護車送往將軍澳醫院治理。"},{"pid":"7125eba5527a52c8dc5d4e639f5cc09a23abd009","tid":1190691,"uid":7043,"like":1231,"dislike":5,"score":1226,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T13:04:18.000Z","msg":"好似拍緊戇豆先生咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9245b8ceddd7c1f59a529c315a183db26faaeb6","tid":1190691,"uid":48964,"like":339,"dislike":3,"score":336,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T13:05:07.000Z","msg":"老夫子"},{"pid":"b28f3f9d93f725648daeb9d5edbd4dd6ca067679","tid":1190691,"uid":228963,"like":426,"dislike":2,"score":424,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T13:05:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6b71bd2f0a0e3d5a4f4850a91e448cfb21ac4e33","tid":1190691,"uid":61974,"like":200,"dislike":1,"score":199,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T13:08:25.000Z","msg":"地獄黑仔王"},{"pid":"7039ba5610b1a1f5c4ff7449796faa9dc9038c5e","tid":1190691,"uid":54373,"like":448,"dislike":2,"score":446,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T13:14:49.000Z","msg":"姓吳（49歲）院友更被蜜蜂刺傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c3ace4c8778ca7bb9a3528bb3ed58ac0124ee2d","tid":1190691,"uid":98692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T13:16:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img